```mermaid
flowchart TB
    UI([User Interface])
    ORCHESTRATION([Orchestration Layer<br/>(Recursive Engine, Mode Selector, Memory)])
    AGENTS([Specialized Agents<br/>- Research - Logic - Creativity - Ethics - Optimization])
    MEMORY([Long-Term Memory])
    SYNTH([Response Synthesizer])

    UI -->|User Query| ORCHESTRATION
    ORCHESTRATION -->|Dispatches Tasks| AGENTS
    ORCHESTRATION -->|Loads Context/Memory| MEMORY
    AGENTS -->|Delivers Results| SYNTH
    MEMORY --> ORCHESTRATION
    SYNTH -->|Final Output| UI

